snippet.title: The Storm Guard Launch Teaser
snippet.description:
Lord Commander! Lead the order of the Storm Guard in its mission to protect the realm of men against the invading creatures and defeat the ancient dragon!

Now available on Steam at http://store.steampowered.com/app/409910
